{
  "texts": [
    "Anonymity is likely to increase confidence in expressing viewpoints even if this (viewpoints) are not palatable to managers or other colleagues.",
    "Increased trust is the main expected benefit.",
    "Anonymity could allow hurtful and controversial comments which would not have been used if linked to a person.",
    "The purpose and necessity for an ombudsman in a requirement elicitation team is not obvious.",
    "Very useful for fast and economic resolution rather than going to law."
  ]
}